
Is there space available for us?! He would not give up at all.
This is his message to himself.
I know you working hard to make ends meet and do the impossible, and you must face the fact that nothing cannot stop you.
People are very jealous of your good heart and expensive, rare talents.
They envy your blunder and every imperfection they see is like some kind of uniqueness to them available for us!
Is there space available for us?! I am Slim Shady. Yes, I am the Real Slim Shady. So stop hesitating, so if you want the Slim Shady, please, stand up!